1366
01:15:35,297 --> 01:15:36,799
YES!!

1367
01:15:36,866 --> 01:15:38,267
WAY TO RIDE COWBOY!

1368
01:15:38,334 --> 01:15:39,869
YES, HA HA!!

1369
01:15:39,935 --> 01:15:41,670
GOOD BOY. YES!

1370
01:15:41,737 --> 01:15:43,706
