1384
01:16:33,355 --> 01:16:34,890
I THINK IT'S IMPORTANT,

1385
01:16:34,957 --> 01:16:36,492
AND I'D LIKE YOU
TO LISTEN BECAUSE

1386
01:16:36,559 --> 01:16:39,762
