1387
01:16:39,829 --> 01:16:41,363
YOU SEE, GOD LOVES YOU,

1388
01:16:41,430 --> 01:16:43,532
AND THE BIBLE SAYS THAT,
"GOD SO LOVED THE WORLD

1389
01:16:43,599 --> 01:16:45,901
THAT HE GAVE HIS
ONLY BEGOTTEN SON

1390
01:16:45,968 --> 01:16:47,470
THAT WHOSOEVER BELIEVETH IN HIM

1391
01:16:47,536 --> 01:16:49,839
