OF SIN IS DEATH.

1395
01:16:57,446 --> 01:16:59,682
THAT'S THE PENALTY
FOR BREAKING GOD'S LAW,

1396
01:16:59,748 --> 01:17:01,484
AND SIN IS DISOBEDIENCE.

1397
01:17:01,550 --> 01:17:10,893
[many people talking--country
dance-band in background]

