1401
01:17:18,934 --> 01:17:20,970
SMOKEY, YOU PROMISED.

1402
01:17:21,036 --> 01:17:23,072
YOU GAVE ME YOUR WORD.

1403
01:17:27,142 --> 01:17:29,512
I PROMISED I'D HELP
YOU RIDE A BULL.

1404
01:17:29,578 --> 01:17:32,114
I DON'T MIND TELLIN' YOU
THAT LAST FEW DAYS

1405
01:17:32,181 --> 01:17:34,884
HAVE BEEN KINDA ROUGH ON ME.

1406
01:17:34,950 --> 01:17:37,319
BUT YOU'RE HERE.

1407
01:17:37,386 --> 01:17:40,022
LET ME GET
THIS STRAIGHT SON.

1408
01:17:40,089 --> 01:17:41,857
DID THIS MAN
PROMISE YOU SOMETHING?

1409
01:17:41,924 --> 01:17:43,826
YEAH--HE PROMISED
HE'D COME

1410
01:17:43,893 --> 01:17:46,395
TO THE COWBOY CHAPEL
