TO TAKE YOU

1417
01:18:02,778 --> 01:18:04,747
TO THE TENT
NEXT DOOR AFTER THE RODEO?

1418
01:18:04,813 --> 01:18:07,449
YUP.

1419
01:18:07,516 --> 01:18:10,452
THAT RIGHT COWBOY?

1420
01:18:10,519 --> 01:18:13,889
♪  ♪

1421
01:18:13,956 --> 01:18:16,292
