GOD LOVES YOU,

1424
01:18:22,665 --> 01:18:24,400
AND GOD IS WILLING
TO FORGIVE YOU.

1425
01:18:24,466 --> 01:18:27,269
BUT YOU'VE GOT TO BE WILLING
TO COME TO GOD--

1426
01:18:27,336 --> 01:18:29,471
HIS WAY.

1427
01:18:29,538 --> 01:18:32,474
JESUS SAID, "I AM THE WAY,
THE TRUTH, AND THE LIFE.

1428
01:18:32,541 --> 01:18:34,977
NO MAN COMES UNTO
THE FATHER BUT BY ME."

1429
01:18:35,044 --> 01:18:37,913
JESUS IS THE ONLY ONE WHO HAS
PAID THE PENALTY OF SIN.

1430
01:18:37,980 --> 01:18:40,916
AND OUTSIDE OF CHRIST, THERE'S
NO WAY YOU CAN STAND BEFORE GOD

1431
01:18:40,983 --> 01:18:42,851
BECAUSE YOU HAVE SINNED.

1432
01:18:42,918 --> 01:18:45,120
AND YOU SAY, "WELL,
WHAT DO YOU MEAN BY SIN?"

1433
01:18:45,187 --> 01:18:49,024
TELLING A LIE IS A SIN.

