01:18:54,930 --> 01:18:58,901
TAKING SOMETHING THAT DOESN'T
BELONG TO YOU IS A SIN.

1436
01:18:58,968 --> 01:19:02,671
AND WHEN CHRIST DIED ON THAT
CROSS 2000 YEARS AGO,

1437
01:19:02,738 --> 01:19:05,207
HE TOOK YOUR SIN,
AND HE TOOK MY SIN,

1438
01:19:05,274 --> 01:19:08,510
AND HE DIED IN YOUR PLACE,
AND IN MY PLACE,

1439
01:19:08,577 --> 01:19:11,580
AND YOU SEE
GOD WILL FORGIVE YOU.

1440
01:19:11,647 --> 01:19:13,616
I DON'T CARE WHAT YOU'VE DONE.

1441
01:19:13,682 --> 01:19:15,117
GOD IS WILLING TO FORGIVE YOU

1442
01:19:15,184 --> 01:19:16,919
IF YOU'RE WILLING TO CALL

1443
01:19:16,986 --> 01:19:19,388
UPON THE NAME OF
THE LORD JESUS CHRIST.

1444
01:19:19,455 --> 01:19:20,856
GOD WILL CLEANSE YOU,

1445
01:19:20,923 --> 01:19:23,792
AND GOD WILL PUT THE PIECES OF
YOUR LIFE BACK TOGETHER.

1446
01:19:23,859 --> 01:19:25,828
I DON'T CARE WHAT YOU'VE DONE.

1447
01:19:25,894 --> 01:19:28,163
AND I WANT TO GIVE YOU
THAT CHANCE TONIGHT--

1448
01:19:28,230 --> 01:19:30,566
IS TO FIND GOD'S PURPOSE
FOR YOUR LIFE,

1449
01:19:30,633 --> 01:19:32,401
GOD'S PLAN FOR YOUR LIFE,

1450
01:19:32,468 --> 01:19:34,570
TO RECEIVE JESUS CHRIST
BY FAITH INTO YOUR HEART,

1451
01:19:34,637 --> 01:19:37,506
AND TO SAY, "GOD, I'VE SINNED,
