1452
01:19:37,573 --> 01:19:39,408
I BELIEVE THAT
YOUR SON JESUS CHRIST

1453
01:19:39,475 --> 01:19:41,010
DIED ON THE CROSS FOR MY SINS,

1454
01:19:41,076 --> 01:19:43,779
AND ON THE THIRD DAY,
YOU RAISED HIM FROM THE DEAD,

1455
01:19:43,846 --> 01:19:45,381
AND THAT HE IS IN HEAVEN.

1456
01:19:45,447 --> 01:19:47,683
AND I WANT TO PUT
MY FAITH AND TRUST IN HIM.

1457
01:19:47,750 --> 01:19:49,718
IF YOU WOULD LIKE
TO DO THAT TONIGHT,

1458
01:19:49,785 --> 01:19:51,420
