1459
01:19:51,487 --> 01:19:53,956
JUST TO GET UP OUT OF YOUR SEAT
AND COME STAND HERE,

1460
01:19:54,023 --> 01:19:56,558
AND THEN I'M GOING TO
LEAD YOU IN A PRAYER.

1461
01:19:56,625 --> 01:19:59,061
WOULD YOU DO THAT RIGHT NOW,
WHEREVER YOU ARE.

1462
01:19:59,128 --> 01:20:01,063
IF GOD IS SPEAKING TO YOU,

1463
01:20:01,130 --> 01:20:02,731
JUST GET UP OUT OF YOUR SEAT,

1464
01:20:02,798 --> 01:20:04,733
AND COME STAND RIGHT HERE,

1465
01:20:04,800 --> 01:20:07,803
AND I'LL HAVE A WORD OF PRAYER
WITH YOU. YOU COME.

1466
01:20:07,870 --> 01:20:13,642
♪  ♪

